#: mixins/grading.py:72
msgid "We could not execute your query; please try again."
msgstr ""
"No hem pogut executar la teva consulta; si us plau, intenta-ho de nou."

#: mixins/grading.py:89
msgid "Weight"
msgstr "Pes"

#: mixins/grading.py:91
msgid "This assigns an integer value representing the weight of this problem"
msgstr "Això assigna un valor enter que representa el pes d’aquest problema"

#: mixins/grading.py:170
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Nom per mostrar"

#: mixins/grading.py:171
msgid "The display name for this component."
msgstr "El nom que es mostra per aquest component."

#: mixins/grading.py:172
msgid "SQL Problem"
msgstr "Problema SQL"

#: mixins/grading.py:176
msgid "Dataset"
msgstr "Conjunt de dades"

#: mixins/grading.py:177
msgid "Which initial dataset/database to be used for queries"
msgstr ""
"Quin conjunt de dades/base de dades inicial s’utilitzarà per a les consultes"

#: mixins/grading.py:183
msgid "Answer Query"
msgstr "Consulta de resposta"

#: mixins/grading.py:184
msgid "A correct response SQL query"
msgstr "Una consulta SQL de resposta correcta"

#: mixins/grading.py:190
msgid "Verify Query"
msgstr "Verifica la consulta"

#: mixins/grading.py:192
msgid ""
"A secondary verification SQL query, to be used if the answer_query modifies "
"the database (UPDATE, INSERT, DELETE, etc.). Only enter a single SELECT "
"query here, which is used for matching the answer"
msgstr ""
"Una consulta SQL de verificació secundària, que s’utilitzarà si la consulta "
"de resposta modifica la base de dades (UPDATE, INSERT, DELETE, etc.). Només "
"introdueix una consulta SELECT aquí, que s’utilitza per comparar la resposta"

#: mixins/grading.py:202
msgid "Modification query statements"
msgstr "Sentències de consulta de modificació"

#: mixins/grading.py:204
msgid ""
"Optional SQL statements, to be executed after the user-submitted query, but "
"before the verify_query."
msgstr ""
"Sentències SQL opcionals, per executar-se després de la consulta enviada per"
" l’usuari, però abans de la consulta de verificació."

#: mixins/grading.py:212
msgid "Is Ordered?"
msgstr "Està ordenat?"

#: mixins/grading.py:213
msgid "Should results be in order?"
msgstr "Els resultats han d’estar ordenats?"

#: mixins/grading.py:228
msgid "Prompt"
msgstr "Indicació"

#: mixins/grading.py:229
msgid "Explanatory text to accompany the problem"
msgstr "Text explicatiu per acompanyar el problema"

#: mixins/grading.py:234
msgid "Submission Query"
msgstr "Consulta de presentació"

#: mixins/grading.py:235
msgid "A Submission Query"
msgstr "Una consulta de presentació"

#: templates/view.html:6
#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"            %(score_weighted)s/%(max_score)s point (graded)\n"
"        "
msgid_plural ""
"\n"
"            %(score_weighted)s/%(max_score)s points (graded)\n"
"        "
msgstr[0] ""
"\n"
"            %(score_weighted)s/%(max_score)s punt (avaluat)\n"
"        "
msgstr[1] ""
"\n"
"            %(score_weighted)s/%(max_score)s punts (avaluats)\n"
"        "

#: templates/view.html:12
msgid "0 points (ungraded)"
msgstr "0 punts (no avaluat)"

#: templates/view.html:21
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "Nota:"

#: templates/view.html:22
msgid ""
"Your queries are executed using SQLite, so you must conform to the SQL "
"constructs supported by SQLite."
msgstr ""
"Les teves consultes s'executen utilitzant SQLite, així que has d'ajustar-te "
"als constructs SQL suportats per SQLite."

#: templates/view.html:27
msgid "Press ESC then TAB or click outside of the code editor to exit"
msgstr "Prem ESC, després TAB, o fes clic fora de l'editor de codi per sortir"

#: templates/view.html:33
msgid "Submit"
msgstr "Envia"

#: templates/view.html:40
msgid "Show Answer"
msgstr "Mostra la resposta"

#: templates/view.html:50
msgid "Correct"
msgstr "Correcte"

#: templates/view.html:52
msgid "Incorrect"
msgstr "Incorrecte"

#: templates/view.html:55
msgid "Unanswered"
msgstr "Sense resposta"

#: templates/view.html:63
msgid ""
"To check your data modification statement, we ran the following query after "
"your modification:"
msgstr ""
"Per comprovar la teva instrucció de modificació de dades, hem executat la "
"següent consulta després de la teva modificació:"

#: templates/view.html:75
msgid "Your Query Result:"
msgstr "El resultat de la teva consulta:"

#: templates/view.html:80
msgid "Expected Query Result:"
msgstr "Resultat esperat de la consulta:"
